SUMMARY:South Howard Flood Relief Project OPEN HOUSE
LOCATION:3111 W. Morrison Avenue Tampa \, FL 33629 United States
DESCRIPTION:We hope youll join us for the South Howard Flood Relief Projec
 t OPEN HOUSE on Thursday\, March 5\, from 6 - 8 PM at Bayshore Baptist Chu
 rch. As the project moves through the early design phase\, this is a great
  opportunity for residents\, businesses\, and stakeholders to connect dire
 ctly with the design-build team. Stop by to learn more about whats being p
 lanned\, share your feedback\, and have your questions answered one-on-one
  by the experts. We hope to see you there! To learn more\, visit: SHstormw
 ater.com (https:shstormwater.com) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/nod
 e/185706
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/185706
END:VEVENT
