SUMMARY:Historic 7th Avenue Bricking Project - Phase 2 Community Meeting
LOCATION:1805 E. 7th Avenue Tampa \, FL 33578 United States
DESCRIPTION:The Next Chapter of Ybors 7th Avenue Is Being Written in Brick
  Join the Tampa Community Redevelopment Agency (CRA) for a community meeti
 ng to learn more about the additional planned bricking work on 7th Avenue 
 between N. 17th and 19th Streets. This is an opportunity for residents\, b
 usiness owners\, and community members to learn more about whats to come f
