SUMMARY:Art Show on The Tampa EDITIONs Roof with Keya Tama
LOCATION:500 Channelside Drive Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Immerse Yourself in The Art Show featuring Keya Tama at The Ta
 mpa EDITION on Friday\, March 27 at 8pm. Created by Keya Tama\, Tied by Ti
 me\, brings together a series of paintings and tapestries that explore how
  meaning emerges through repetition\, attention and time. Rooted in geomet
 ric abstraction and restrained figuration\, the works will explore the sub
 tle systems that shape human experience the same as those found in nature\
 , built environments\, and shared social structures. Following the exhibit
 ion\, the celebration will continue with a live DJ and after-party at Arts
  Club on the second floor of The Tampa EDITION\, with light bites and cock
 tails. The art show is free to attend\, and food and drinks are available 
 for purchase. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187576
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/187576
END:VEVENT
