DESCRIPTION:The Opulence Day Party is the celebratory grand finale of Opul
 ence Experience Weekend  a high-energy\, joy-forward gathering rooted in m
 usic\, culture\, and collective release. This daytime celebration centers 
 Black and Brown queer community while welcoming all who move with respect 
 and intention. Expect elevated vibes\, intentional sound\, and a dance flo
 or powered by connection as we close the weekend together in full expressi
 on. Sounds by:  DJ Xsa (DC)  T-Couture Special Live Performance:  Aja Iman
