 igital Signage in Tampas Downtown before a city council workshop on April 
 7. This public input meeting will outline the suggested design guidelines\
 , policies and incorporation of art and placemaking. It is an opportunity 
 to share your thoughts and ideas. Your feedback will help guide how digita
 l signage fits into Tampas evolving urban landscape. Hosted by the Tampa D
 owntown Partnership Wednesday\, April 1 5-6:30pm Barrymore Hotel Tampa Riv
 erwalk (Room: Monarch B) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187486
